{"tid":256276,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[經典再現]三十年後再起飛 湯佬證實《Top Gun 2》下年開拍","createTime":"2017-05-24T11:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T17:46:01.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e804395cf734478f58b3fe0751fc1c7cd295f38","tid":256276,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"30年前嘅《壯志凌雲(Top Gun)》為世人帶黎兩樣嘢，第一係MA-1軍褸，第二就係當年靚仔到過哂火嘅Tom Cruise。時隔三十年，《Top Gun》已經成為唔少人嘅最愛電影，Tom Cruise都由「靚仔湯」變「靚佬湯」，而佢近日就向傳媒確認即將開拍續集！仲會下年就開鏡添！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/portal/201705/24/185850cuaz3ybaag21u3hh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fportal%2F201705%2F24%2F185850cuaz3ybaag21u3hh.jpg&h=cb0da5ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早於上年1月，《壯》嘅監製就喺Twitter發佈與靚佬湯嘅合照，仲話兩個人傾過下開拍《壯》續集之事，當時已經引黎Fans熱切期待。接下來嘅時間靚佬湯亦多次表示真係討論當中。去到近日，於澳洲宣傳《盜墓迷城(Mummy)》嘅靚佬湯就於電視節目上明言「(續集)肯定會發生」，「我們大概會於明年開拍&hellip;你是我第一個告訴的人！」\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然選角、導演甚至劇情等就未有進一步消息，但當年飾演Tom Cruise「宿敵」Iceman嘅Val Kilmer就曾經於今年四月嘅一個訪問中表示自己會參演《Top Gun 2》，所以絕對值得大家期待！"},{"pid":"e2e76dd54a863334f409985b34604701cfbec5dc","tid":256276,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"湯老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8159700fead378d11cbcf5c71bdc2c9989b3c556","tid":256276,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qph.ec.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-40a850cc45af3576ce339b4460d56134-c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.ec.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-40a850cc45af3576ce339b4460d56134-c&h=b7f3178f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor